{"id":1734902,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:05.717Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734902,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Dengan Lafaz Bismillah","overview":"# The Story of Mak Seri  The story of Mak Seri (Normah Damanhuri) living alone in the village after her husband's death. Only Jamilah is someone she can confide in and express her feelings of longing and disappointment towards her daughter Zaleha. Zaleha (Tiz Zaqyah) resents her because of a marriage without her consent, but on the contrary, the marriage hides Zaleha's secret that she was already pregnant with an illegitimate child. For Mak Seri, what she did was the best for her daughter. Although Zaleha does not express her feelings, Mak Seri knows that Lokman (Izzue Islam) is not her heart's choice. Until now Mak Seri knows that Zaleha still cannot accept Lokman in her heart. Meanwhile, Zaleha is very disappointed because she cannot be with Johari (Iqram Dinzly), the beloved son of the village chief, without Mak Seri's knowledge until news of her pregnancy is discovered. Mak Seri forces Zaleha to be honest but Zaleha remains silent, unable to speak.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/749J0kFPPhL1859GLWrcWpwZDcV.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Dengan Lafaz Bismillah","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1289050,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Tiz Zaqyah","original_name":"Tiz Zaqyah","popularity":0.4847,"profile_path":"/6XEyFXqw7kvcknBeg9IifYhNFn3.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5e88600c0fead81d21f528","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1276750,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Izzue Isl